subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Landry Jones outplayed Christian Ponder by throwing for 380 yards and 4 touchdowns, and No. 10 Oklahoma moved past a shaky season opener with a 47-17 victory against No. 17 Florida State at home Saturday.
